It must be on the HSS list, and must be numbered 100-199. It can not be within an engineering department. If Anthro 122A is listed, then it counts. 

We pull from the Letters and Sciences breadth lists, but not the Biological or Physical Science lists.  If your prospective course appears on these two lists (and not on any of the other accepted lists), we cannot accept it as fulfilling an H/SS requirement. When in doubt, please contact your ESS Advisor to check.
